# radroots_nostr_runtime

Nostr runtime primitives and orchestration interfaces for the Rad Roots SDK.

## Goals

- define stable runtime interfaces for events, subscriptions, and connections
- keep runtime orchestration behavior deterministic across supported environments
- support feature-gated client and async runtime integration surfaces
- provide reusable runtime primitives for higher-level Rad Roots crates

